      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为团队整理一份Mermaid流程图的形状速查表，方便大家快速识别不同节点类型。从左到右排列，你觉得怎么样？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "flowchart LR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，横向布局比较清晰。我先从基础形状开始，第一个是标准矩形，用方括号表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A[Rectangle]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，接下来放圆角矩形，这个常用于表示开始或结束节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B(Rounded)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加圆角矩形。然后我想放体育场形状，就是两边半圆的那种，用圆括号加方括号组合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C([Stadium])"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，体育场形状是([Stadium])这样吗？我记得是双括号里面包方括号？不对，你写的是圆括号加方括号，让我确认一下语法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C([Stadium])"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，圆括号包裹方括号，([Stadium])，这样渲染出来就是跑道形的体育场样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C([Stadium])"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "明白了。接下来加子程序形状，双边框的矩形，用于表示预定义流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D[[Subroutine]]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "子程序已添加，用双方括号[[Subroutine]]。然后是数据库形状，圆柱体那种。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E[(Database)]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据库之后放圆形，用双层圆括号。这个简单，但容易和椭圆形混淆。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "F((Circle))"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "圆形已添加。接下来我想放旗帜形状，用于标记目标或里程碑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GFlag]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "旗帜的语法好像不对，你写的是Flag]，但左边应该是尖括号，右边应该是花括号？不对，让我想想，旗帜应该是Flag]这样，但右边应该是花括号闭合？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GFlag]"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我搞混了。旗帜的正确语法是Flag]，左边尖括号，右边方括号。但这样渲染出来旗帜的旗杆在右边。让我修正为Flag]。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GFlag]"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，最终是Flag]对吗？尖括号开头，方括号结尾。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GFlag]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，已修正。接下来是菱形判断框，用花括号。",
