      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后是六边形，准备表示准备或预处理步骤，用双花括号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "I{{Hexagon}}"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "六边形已添加。现在进入平行四边形系列，第一个是左斜右直的，表示输入输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
